==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prediction
<hw>Pre*dic"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>praedictio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>pr⟦eacute⟧diction</ets>.]</ety>
<def>The act of foretelling; also, that which is foretold;
prophecy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>predictions</qex> of cold and long winters.</q>
<rj><qau>Bacon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Prophecy; prognostication; foreboding; augury;
divination; soothsaying; vaticination.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Predictional</ent>⟦br⟧
